title: David Baldacci - Simple Genius
description: A three-hour drive from Washington, D.C., two clandestine institutions face each other across a heavily guarded river. One is the world&#039;s most unusual laboratory, whose goals and funding are a mystery. The other is an elite CIA training camp shrouded in secrecy. Now a man and a woman are about to run a gauntlet between these two puzzle factories, straight into a furious struggle to exploit a potentially world-shattering discovery--and keep some other secrets underwraps forever...2008
